{"title":"Set the alarm for 23:000","description":"Turn on the alarm clock on 23:000 with sound. 23 hours 00 minutes  alarm clock. Free and simple alarm online. Set alarm for 23 hours 00 minutes .","content":"Is there a need to set an alarm for 23 hours 00 minutes ? Use our simple and free alarm clock online! \nSet the alarm for 23 hours 00 minutes  or choose another time by setting it yourself or by selecting from the list. An alarm clock with a sound that you can set yourself. After setting the time, press the **Add** button to turn on the alarm.\n\nTurn on the alarm clock for 23 hours 00 minutes  and go about your business, the alarm clock will definitely notify you at exactly 23:000.\n\nAll alarms are saved in your browser, so you can reuse them. The clock beautifully shows the time remaining from 23 hours 00 minutes , with an accuracy of seconds and milliseconds."}